Name: criteria_for_individuals_directly_served
Hint__c:
Count the entire population of the village or community if the identified crossing/proposed bridge site is the only route from the village or community to any of the following:
- Primary school
- Secondary school
- Clinic, health center, or hospital
- Market that is attended by members of the village at least weekly for some part of the year (if it’s a weekly market that only occurs seasonally, still count it)
- Significant local employer or labor opportunities (examples include commercial farms or plantations, agricultural processing centers, or wage-labor opportunities in construction, brick-making, tree-cutting, transportation, or domestic work)
- Road or transportation connection point to nearest urban area
